Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.12,0:24:52.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}十分な喪失と招待され
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.18,0:24:54.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Today's program is a tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.56,0:24:58.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}救済の一切もない名作を
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.81,0:25:04.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Please be quiet. Hope is noisy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.58,0:25:08.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The dreams rot off and drop away
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.76,0:25:11.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}望みこそ腐敗の元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.92,0:25:14.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No wish, no smile, only despair
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.79,0:25:18.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The curtain will open
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.87,0:25:21.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Welcome to the party
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.78,0:25:25.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}暗闇で舞う無数の影よ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.53,0:25:28.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This show will never end
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.46,0:25:35.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何人も逃れられはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.70,0:24:48.13,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这张票是我已失去的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.12,0:24:52.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是让人失去一切的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.18,0:24:54.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天在上演的是一出悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.56,0:24:58.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是毫无救济的名作
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.81,0:25:04.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望过于嘈杂  请安静
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.58,0:25:08.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那些幻梦早已消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.76,0:25:11.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望正是腐败的元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.92,0:25:14.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}禁止许愿  禁止欢笑  只有绝望
